(12340,	20,	3,	'Lexus RC',	'Introducing the Lexus RC, a captivating coupe that seamlessly blends luxury, performance, and cutting-edge technology to create an unforgettable driving experience. As one of Lexus\' most iconic models, the RC embodies the brand\'s commitment to craftsmanship, innovation, and uncompromising quality.\r\n\r\nAt first glance, the Lexus RC captivates with its striking design and athletic stance. With its sculpted lines, aggressive grille, and distinctive LED headlights, the RC exudes an aura of sophistication and dynamism that is unmistakably Lexus. Every detail, from the aerodynamic bodywork to the premium finishes and elegant accents, is meticulously crafted to enhance both performance and visual appeal, making the RC a true work of art on wheels.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'re greeted by a cabin that is both luxurious and technologically advanced. Premium materials such as leather, wood, and aluminum adorn every surface, creating an ambiance of refinement and comfort. The driver-focused cockpit puts all essential controls within easy reach, while advanced technology features such as the Lexus Enform infotainment system keep you connected and entertained on the go. With its spacious interior and comfortable seating, the RC offers a driving experience that is both exhilarating and luxurious, whether you\'re cruising through city streets or embarking on a weekend getaway.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s under the hood where the Lexus RC truly shines. With a range of powerful and efficient engine options to choose from, including turbocharged four-cylinder and V6 options, the RC delivers exhilarating performance that is sure to thrill even the most discerning drivers. Whether accelerating from a standstill or navigating winding mountain roads, the RC offers responsive handling, precise steering, and a refined ride quality that is second to none.',	'2024-07-01 04:04:00',	'images/LEXUS RC.png.jpg'),
(12341,	20,	3,	'Porsche 911',	'Introducing the Porsche 911, an iconic sports car that has captivated enthusiasts around the world for generations. Renowned for its timeless design, unparalleled performance, and legendary heritage, the 911 represents the epitome of Porsche\'s commitment to automotive excellence.\r\n\r\nAt first glance, the Porsche 911 commands attention with its unmistakable silhouette and distinctive design cues. With its rear-engine layout, sloping roofline, and muscular rear fenders, the 911 exudes an aura of power and athleticism that is instantly recognizable. Every aspect of the design is engineered to optimize aerodynamic efficiency and enhance performance, from the sleek bodywork to the iconic round headlights, making the 911 a true symbol of automotive excellence.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'re greeted by a cockpit that is designed with the driver in mind. High-quality materials such as leather, Alcantara, and carbon fiber adorn every surface, creating an ambiance of luxury and performance. The driver-centric layout puts all essential controls within easy reach, while advanced technology features such as the Porsche Communication Management (PCM) system keep you connected and entertained on the go. With its comfortable seating and intuitive interface, the 911 offers a driving experience that is both exhilarating and refined, whether you\'re tearing up the track or cruising through city streets.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s under the hood where the Porsche 911 truly shines. With a range of powerful and efficient engine options to choose from, including turbocharged flat-six and hybrid options, the 911 delivers breathtaking performance that is sure to leave you speechless. Whether accelerating from a standstill or tackling hairpin turns, the 911 offers blistering acceleration, razor-sharp handling, and precise steering that make every drive a thrill.',	'2024-08-04 04:04:00',	'images/porse_911.png.jpg'),
(12342,	20,	3,	'Ford Mustang',	'Introducing the Ford Mustang, a legendary muscle car that has been an icon of American automotive culture for over five decades. With its bold design, powerful performance, and unmistakable presence, the Mustang embodies the spirit of freedom, adventure, and exhilaration on the open road.\r\n\r\nFrom the moment you lay eyes on it, the Ford Mustang captivates with its timeless design and unmistakable silhouette. With its long hood, short deck, and iconic fastback profile, the Mustang exudes an aura of strength and performance that is instantly recognizable. Every detail, from the distinctive grille to the signature tri-bar taillights, pays homage to the Mustang\'s rich heritage while also signaling its modernity and relevance in today\'s automotive landscape.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'re greeted by a cabin that blends retro-inspired design cues with modern amenities and technology. Premium materials such as leather, aluminum, and carbon fiber adorn every surface, creating an atmosphere of refinement and comfort. The driver-centric cockpit puts all essential controls within easy reach, while advanced technology features such as the SYNC infotainment system keep you connected and entertained on the go. With its comfortable seating and spacious interior, the Mustang offers a driving experience that is both exhilarating and comfortable, whether you\'re cruising down the highway or tackling twisty backroads.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s under the hood where the Ford Mustang truly comes to life. With a range of powerful engine options to choose from, including turbocharged four-cylinder, V6, and V8 options, the Mustang delivers exhilarating performance that is sure to get your adrenaline pumping. Whether accelerating from a standstill or carving through corners, the Mustang offers responsive handling, precise steering, and a thrilling exhaust note that make every drive an unforgettable experience.',	'2024-07-07 04:04:00',	'images/mustang_ford.png.jpg'),
(12343,	20,	5,	'Chevrolet Tahoe',	'Introducing the Chevrolet Tahoe, a rugged and versatile SUV that has been a staple of American roads for decades. Renowned for its spacious interior, robust performance, and unmatched towing capabilities, the Tahoe represents the epitome of reliability, comfort, and capability.\r\n\r\nAt first glance, the Chevrolet Tahoe commands attention with its bold and imposing presence. With its muscular lines, aggressive grille, and distinctive LED headlights, the Tahoe exudes an aura of strength and confidence that is unmistakably Chevrolet. Whether navigating through city streets or traversing rugged terrain, the Tahoe\'s rugged design and commanding stance make it a formidable presence on the road.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'re greeted by a cavernous interior that offers ample space for passengers and cargo alike. With seating for up to eight passengers and a versatile cargo area, the Tahoe is perfectly suited for family road trips, weekend adventures, and everything in between. Premium materials and thoughtful design details create an atmosphere of comfort and refinement, while advanced technology features such as the Chevrolet Infotainment System keep you connected and entertained on the go.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s under the hood where the Chevrolet Tahoe truly shines. With a powerful V8 engine and available four-wheel drive, the Tahoe delivers robust performance and impressive towing capabilities that make it ideal for hauling trailers, boats, and other recreational equipment. Whether towing a boat to the lake or navigating through heavy snow, the Tahoe offers the performance and capability you need to tackle any challenge with confidence.\r\n\r\nIn addition to its impressive performance, the Chevrolet Tahoe also comes equipped with a range of advanced safety features and driver assistance technologies to help keep you and your passengers safe on the road. From forward collision alert to lane departure warning, the Tahoe offers peace of mind that you\'re protected from unexpected hazards and accidents, allowing you to focus on enjoying the journey ahead.\r\n\r\nIn conclusion, the Chevrolet Tahoe is more than just an SUV – it\'s a symbol of American ingenuity, versatility, and dependability. With its rugged design, spacious interior, and robust performance, the Tahoe offers a driving experience that is both practical and enjoyable, whether you\'re cruising through the city or exploring the great outdoors. So why settle for anything less? Experience the Chevrolet Tahoe and discover the true meaning of American SUV excellence.',	'2024-08-08 04:04:00',	'images/CHEVROLET TAHOE.jpg'),
