(12346,	21,	1,	'Volkswagen Golf',	'Introducing the Volkswagen Golf Estate, a versatile and practical wagon that combines the timeless design and dynamic performance of the Golf with added cargo space and flexibility. As one of Volkswagen\'s most iconic models, the Golf Estate offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and functionality, making it the ideal choice for drivers who require ample cargo capacity without compromising on driving enjoyment.\r\n\r\nAt first glance, the Volkswagen Golf Estate impresses with its sleek and contemporary design. With its clean lines, refined proportions, and distinctive front grille, the Golf Estate exudes an understated elegance that is both timeless and modern. The elongated roofline and extended rear overhang hint at the generous cargo space within, while the bold character lines and sculpted bodywork add a touch of sportiness to its appearance.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'ll find a spacious and well-appointed interior that is designed with both driver and passengers in mind. Premium materials, soft-touch surfaces, and ergonomic controls create an inviting and comfortable atmosphere, while thoughtful design details such as adjustable cargo floor heights and split-folding rear seats enhance versatility and practicality. With ample legroom, headroom, and storage compartments throughout the cabin, the Golf Estate offers unmatched flexibility for carrying passengers and cargo alike.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s on the road where the Volkswagen Golf Estate truly shines. With a range of efficient and responsive engine options to choose from, including turbocharged petrol and diesel engines, the Golf Estate delivers dynamic performance and agile handling that make every drive a pleasure. Whether navigating through city streets or cruising along the highway, the Golf Estate offers smooth acceleration, precise steering, and a composed ride quality that instills confidence in all driving conditions.\r\n\r\nIn addition to its impressive performance, the Volkswagen Golf Estate also comes equipped with a range of advanced safety features and driver assistance technologies to help keep you and your passengers safe on the road. From adaptive cruise control to lane-keeping assist, the Golf Estate offers peace of mind that you\'re protected from unexpected hazards and accidents, allowing you to focus on enjoying the journey ahead.',	'2024-09-07 03:03:00',	'images/volkswagen Golf.jpg.jpg'),
(12347,	21,	2,	'Hyundai Kona ',	'Introducing the Hyundai Kona Electric, a groundbreaking crossover SUV that combines the practicality and versatility of the Kona with the efficiency and eco-friendliness of electric power. As one of Hyundai\'s most innovative models, the Kona Electric represents the future of sustainable mobility, offering drivers an emissions-free driving experience without sacrificing performance, style, or comfort.\r\n\r\nAt first glance, the Hyundai Kona Electric stands out with its bold and futuristic design. With its sleek silhouette, sculpted lines, and distinctive LED lighting signature, the Kona Electric exudes an aura of sophistication and modernity that is unmistakably Hyundai. The closed grille, aerodynamic bodywork, and unique alloy wheel designs not only enhance its visual appeal but also optimize efficiency and range, making the Kona Electric as practical as it is stylish.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'re greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior that is designed for both driver and passengers. Premium materials, ergonomic controls, and intuitive technology features create an inviting and comfortable atmosphere, while thoughtful design details such as adjustable seating positions and ample cargo space ensure versatility and practicality for all your needs. With its generous legroom, headroom, and storage compartments throughout the cabin, the Kona Electric offers unmatched flexibility for carrying passengers and cargo on your journeys.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s on the road where the Hyundai Kona Electric truly shines. Powered by an efficient electric motor and advanced battery technology, the Kona Electric delivers instant torque, smooth acceleration, and whisper-quiet performance that make every drive a delight. With multiple driving modes and regenerative braking settings to choose from, you can tailor your driving experience to suit your preferences and maximize efficiency, while enjoying the benefits of emissions-free motoring.\r\n\r\nIn addition to its impressive performance, the Hyundai Kona Electric also comes equipped with a range of advanced safety features and driver assistance technologies to help keep you and your passengers safe on the road. From forward collision warning to lane-keeping assist, the Kona Electric offers peace of mind that you\'re protected from unexpected hazards and accidents, allowing you to focus on enjoying the quiet, emissions-free driving experience.',	'2024-07-07 04:04:00',	'images/hyundai kona.jpg'),
(12348,	17,	3,	'Audi A5',	'Introducing the Audi A5 Coupe, a sleek and sophisticated grand tourer that combines elegant design, advanced technology, and exhilarating performance to create a driving experience like no other. As one of Audi\'s most iconic models, the A5 Coupe sets the standard for luxury coupes with its timeless styling, refined interior, and dynamic driving dynamics.\r\n\r\nFrom the moment you lay eyes on it, the Audi A5 Coupe captivates with its striking design and athletic proportions. With its flowing lines, sculpted surfaces, and muscular stance, the A5 Coupe exudes an aura of confidence and sophistication that is unmistakably Audi. The iconic Singleframe grille, LED headlights, and bold character lines add a touch of sportiness to its appearance, while the sleek roofline and coupe silhouette give it a sense of elegance and grace.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'re greeted by a luxurious and meticulously crafted interior that is designed to indulge your senses. Premium materials such as leather, aluminum, and wood adorn every surface, creating an ambiance of opulence and refinement. The driver-centric cockpit puts all essential controls within easy reach, while advanced technology features such as the Audi Virtual Cockpit and MMI infotainment system keep you connected and entertained on the go. With its comfortable seating, spacious cabin, and upscale amenities, the A5 Coupe offers a driving experience that is both luxurious and exhilarating, whether you\'re cruising through city streets or carving through winding mountain roads.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s under the hood where the Audi A5 Coupe truly shines. With a range of powerful and efficient engine options to choose from, including turbocharged four-cylinder and V6 options, the A5 Coupe delivers exhilarating performance and dynamic handling that make every drive a thrill. Whether accelerating from a standstill or tackling twisty backroads, the A5 Coupe offers responsive steering, precise handling, and a smooth, refined ride quality that is sure to impress even the most discerning drivers.',	'2024-08-08 04:04:00',	'images/audi 5 coupe.jpg.jpg'),
(12349,	17,	4,	'Volkswagen Passat',	'Introducing the Volkswagen Passat, a refined and versatile sedan that combines German engineering, sophisticated design, and advanced technology to create a driving experience that is both practical and enjoyable. As one of Volkswagen\'s most iconic models, the Passat has earned a reputation for excellence, offering drivers a perfect blend of comfort, performance, and reliability.\r\n\r\nAt first glance, the Volkswagen Passat impresses with its understated elegance and timeless design. With its clean lines, sculpted surfaces, and distinctive front grille, the Passat exudes an aura of sophistication and refinement that is unmistakably Volkswagen. The sleek profile, aerodynamic bodywork, and stylish alloy wheels add a touch of sportiness to its appearance, while the spacious interior and comfortable seating ensure a pleasant journey for both driver and passengers alike.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'ll find a well-appointed interior that is designed with both comfort and convenience in mind. High-quality materials, soft-touch surfaces, and intuitive controls create an inviting and comfortable atmosphere, while thoughtful design details such as adjustable seating positions and ample storage compartments enhance versatility and practicality. With its spacious cabin, generous legroom, and user-friendly technology features, the Passat offers a driving experience that is both comfortable and convenient, whether you\'re commuting to work or embarking on a road trip with family and friends.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s on the road where the Volkswagen Passat truly shines. With a range of efficient and responsive engine options to choose from, including turbocharged petrol and diesel engines, the Passat delivers smooth acceleration, precise handling, and a composed ride quality that instills confidence in all driving conditions. Whether navigating through city streets or cruising along the highway, the Passat offers a refined and enjoyable driving experience that is sure to impress.',	'2024-09-03 01:04:00',	'images/volkswagen Passat sedan.jpg.jpg'),
(12350,	17,	5,	'Jeep Wrangler',	'Introducing the Jeep Wrangler, an iconic off-road SUV that has been conquering trails and exploring the great outdoors for generations. Renowned for its rugged design, legendary capability, and unmatched versatility, the Wrangler represents the epitome of adventure, allowing drivers to venture off the beaten path and experience the freedom of exploration like never before.\r\n\r\nFrom the moment you lay eyes on it, the Jeep Wrangler commands attention with its unmistakable silhouette and iconic design cues. With its seven-slot grille, round headlights, and removable doors and roof, the Wrangler exudes an aura of ruggedness and authenticity that is synonymous with the Jeep brand. The high ground clearance, short overhangs, and robust body-on-frame construction give it the capability to conquer the toughest terrain, while the available four-wheel-drive system and off-road-focused features ensure that no obstacle is too challenging to overcome.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'re greeted by a rugged and functional interior that is designed for adventure. Washable surfaces, drain plugs, and durable materials make it easy to clean and maintain, while thoughtful design details such as removable carpet and folding rear seats enhance versatility and practicality. With its spacious cabin, ample cargo space, and weatherproof controls, the Wrangler offers everything you need to tackle your next outdoor adventure with confidence.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s off the road where the Jeep Wrangler truly comes to life. With a range of powerful engine options to choose from, including a turbocharged four-cylinder and a V6, the Wrangler delivers impressive performance and legendary capability that make it the ultimate off-road machine. Whether crawling over rocks, fording streams, or navigating through mud, the Wrangler offers unmatched traction, ground clearance, and articulation that allow you to tackle any trail with ease.',	'2024-08-08 04:04:00',	'images/jeep wrangler.jpg.png'),
(12351,	23,	2,	' Honda Accord',	'Introducing the Honda Accord, a hallmark of reliability, comfort, and performance in the midsize sedan segment. Renowned for its balanced blend of refinement, practicality, and driving dynamics, the Accord represents the epitome of automotive excellence, catering to drivers seeking a versatile and dependable vehicle for their everyday needs.\r\n\r\nFrom its sleek and aerodynamic exterior to its spacious and well-appointed interior, the Honda Accord exudes sophistication and modernity at every turn. With its clean lines, bold grille, and LED headlights, the Accord strikes a harmonious balance between elegance and athleticism, making a distinct impression on the road.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'ll discover a thoughtfully designed cabin that prioritizes comfort, convenience, and connectivity. Premium materials, ergonomic controls, and intuitive technology features create an inviting and user-friendly environment, while ample legroom, supportive seats, and expansive cargo space ensure that both drivers and passengers alike can travel in utmost comfort.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s on the road where the Honda Accord truly shines. With a choice of efficient yet potent powertrains, including turbocharged four-cylinder and hybrid options, the Accord delivers a responsive and engaging driving experience that\'s both spirited and fuel-efficient. Whether navigating city streets or cruising on the highway, the Accord offers composed handling, refined ride quality, and confident performance that instills a sense of confidence behind the wheel.\r\n\r\nIn addition to its dynamic performance, the Honda Accord comes equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety and driver-assistive technologies to help keep you and your passengers safe on every journey. From collision mitigation braking to adaptive cruise control, the Accord provides peace of mind by actively helping to prevent accidents and mitigate the severity of collisions.\r\n\r\nIn conclusion, the Honda Accord is more than just a sedan – it\'s a versatile and dependable companion that excels in every aspect of modern driving. With its sophisticated design, spacious interior, efficient performance, and advanced safety features, the Accord offers a compelling package that\'s sure to impress discerning drivers. So why settle for anything less? Experience the Honda Accord and discover the perfect balance of style, comfort, and performance for your daily adventures.',	'2024-07-07 04:04:00',	'images/Honda_Accord_(CV3)_EX_eHEV,_2021,_front.jpg'),
(12352,	23,	5,	'Land Rover Range Rover',	'Introducing the Land Rover Range Rover, a pinnacle of luxury and off-road capability that has set the standard for premium SUVs for decades. Renowned for its refined design, uncompromising performance, and unparalleled comfort, the Range Rover represents the epitome of automotive luxury, allowing drivers to explore both urban landscapes and rugged terrain with effortless grace and style.\r\n\r\nFrom the moment you lay eyes on it, the Land Rover Range Rover exudes sophistication and elegance with its sleek silhouette, distinctive floating roof, and signature grille. Crafted from the finest materials and finished with meticulous attention to detail, the Range Rover\'s exterior design showcases a perfect blend of modernity and timeless appeal, making it a true standout on the road.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'re greeted by a sumptuous and meticulously crafted interior that epitomizes luxury and refinement. Premium leather upholstery, handcrafted wood trim, and soft-touch surfaces create an ambiance of opulence and comfort, while advanced technology features such as the Touch Pro Duo infotainment system and configurable ambient lighting elevate the driving experience to new heights of sophistication.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s on the road where the Land Rover Range Rover truly shines. With a range of powerful engine options to choose from, including turbocharged petrol and diesel engines, as well as plug-in hybrid variants, the Range Rover delivers effortless performance and refined driving dynamics that are second to none. Whether cruising on the highway or traversing rugged terrain, the Range Rover offers smooth acceleration, precise steering, and a composed ride quality that instills confidence in any driving situation.\r\n\r\nIn addition to its exceptional on-road performance, the Land Rover Range Rover is also equipped with a suite of advanced off-road technologies and features that allow it to tackle the most challenging terrain with ease. From Terrain Response 2 system to All-Terrain Progress Control, the Range Rover offers unmatched capability and versatility, ensuring that no adventure is out of reach.\r\n\r\nIn conclusion, the Land Rover Range Rover is more than just an SUV – it\'s a symbol of luxury, performance, and adventure. With its exquisite design, luxurious interior, and unmatched capability, the Range Rover offers a driving experience that is truly unparalleled, allowing drivers to explore the world in style and comfort. So why settle for anything less? Experience the Land Rover Range Rover and discover the true meaning of automotive luxury.',	'2024-07-03 04:44:00',	'images/land rangerover .jpg.jpg'),
(12353,	23,	3,	'Toyota Camry ',	'Introducing the Toyota Camry, a quintessential midsize sedan that has been a staple on American roads for generations. Renowned for its reliability, comfort, and value, the Camry represents the epitome of practicality and dependability, catering to drivers seeking a well-rounded and affordable vehicle for their everyday needs.\r\n\r\nFrom its sleek and contemporary exterior design to its spacious and comfortable interior, the Toyota Camry strikes the perfect balance between style and functionality. With its bold grille, expressive lines, and LED headlights, the Camry exudes a sense of modernity and sophistication that commands attention wherever it goes.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'ll find a meticulously crafted cabin that offers a premium and welcoming atmosphere for both driver and passengers. High-quality materials, ergonomic controls, and intuitive technology features create an inviting and user-friendly environment, while spacious seating, ample legroom, and generous cargo capacity ensure that everyone can travel in comfort and style.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s on the road where the Toyota Camry truly shines. With a choice of efficient and responsive powertrains, including fuel-efficient four-cylinder engines and powerful hybrid options, the Camry delivers a smooth and refined driving experience that\'s both enjoyable and economical. Whether cruising on the highway or navigating city streets, the Camry offers responsive handling, confident acceleration, and a composed ride quality that inspires confidence behind the wheel.\r\n\r\nIn addition to its impressive performance, the Toyota Camry is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features and driver-assistive technologies to help keep you and your passengers safe on every journey. From pre-collision braking to lane departure alert, the Camry provides peace of mind by actively helping to prevent accidents and protect occupants in the event of a collision.\r\n',	'2024-06-01 04:02:00',	'images/2024-toyota-camry-102-64cbc4858e198.jpg'),
(12354,	23,	6,	' Chevrolet Camaro',	'Introducing the Chevrolet Camaro, an iconic American muscle car that embodies power, performance, and passion. Renowned for its bold design, exhilarating performance, and unmistakable presence on the road, the Camaro represents the epitome of automotive excitement, catering to enthusiasts seeking a thrilling driving experience like no other.\r\n\r\nFrom its aggressive stance and sculpted body lines to its iconic grille and signature LED headlights, the Chevrolet Camaro commands attention with its unmistakable presence and timeless design cues. With its muscular proportions, aerodynamic profile, and distinctive styling elements, the Camaro exudes an aura of athleticism and confidence that sets it apart from the competition.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'ll discover a driver-focused cockpit that combines retro-inspired design with modern technology and comfort features. Premium materials, ergonomic controls, and intuitive technology interfaces create an immersive driving experience that puts you in complete control, while supportive seating, ample legroom, and advanced connectivity options ensure that every journey is both exhilarating and enjoyable.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s on the road where the Chevrolet Camaro truly comes to life. With a range of powerful engine options to choose from, including turbocharged four-cylinder, V6, and V8 variants, the Camaro delivers heart-pounding performance and dynamic handling that\'s guaranteed to thrill even the most discerning driving enthusiasts. Whether tearing up the track or cruising down the highway, the Camaro offers blistering acceleration, razor-sharp handling, and a spine-tingling exhaust note that ignites the senses and leaves a lasting impression.\r\n\r\nIn addition to its exhilarating performance, the Chevrolet Camaro is also equipped with a host of advanced safety features and driver-assistive technologies to help keep you safe on the road. From rear vision camera to blind-spot monitoring, the Camaro provides peace of mind by actively helping to prevent accidents and protect occupants in the event of a collision.\r\n\r\nIn conclusion, the Chevrolet Camaro is more than just a car – it\'s an icon of American automotive engineering and a symbol of freedom, power, and excitement. With its bold design, exhilarating performance, and advanced technology features, the Camaro offers a driving experience that\'s as thrilling as it is unforgettable. So why settle for anything less? Experience the Chevrolet Camaro and unleash your passion for the open road.',	'2024-09-05 04:04:00',	'images/chervlot camro.jpg.jpg'),
(12355,	23,	3,	'Honda Civic',	'Introducing the Honda Civic Coupe, a stylish and sporty compact car that combines sleek design, dynamic performance, and advanced technology. Renowned for its youthful spirit, practicality, and fun-to-drive nature, the Civic Coupe represents the epitome of automotive versatility, catering to drivers seeking a dynamic and affordable vehicle for their daily adventures.\r\n\r\nFrom its bold and aggressive exterior styling to its sleek profile and aerodynamic lines, the Honda Civic Coupe exudes sporty sophistication and modern appeal. With its distinctive grille, sculpted body panels, and available sport trim options, the Civic Coupe commands attention on the road and stands out from the crowd with its unmistakable presence.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'ll find a driver-centric cockpit that prioritizes comfort, convenience, and connectivity. High-quality materials, intuitive controls, and advanced technology features create a welcoming and ergonomic interior environment that enhances the driving experience, while spacious seating, ample cargo space, and versatile storage solutions ensure that both driver and passengers can travel in comfort and style.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s on the road where the Honda Civic Coupe truly shines. With a choice of efficient and responsive powertrains, including naturally aspirated and turbocharged engines, the Civic Coupe delivers agile handling, precise steering, and spirited performance that\'s perfect for navigating city streets or carving through winding mountain roads. Whether commuting to work or embarking on a weekend adventure, the Civic Coupe offers dynamic driving dynamics and a responsive ride quality that\'s sure to put a smile on your face.\r\n\r\nIn addition to its engaging performance, the Honda Civic Coupe is also equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features and driver-assistive technologies to help keep you safe on every journey. From collision mitigation braking to adaptive cruise control, the Civic Coupe provides peace of mind by actively helping to prevent accidents and protect occupants in the event of a collision.',	'2024-09-05 04:05:00',	'images/honda civic.jpg'),
(12356,	19,	7,	'Aston Martin Vantage:',	'Introducing the Aston Martin Vantage, a timeless and exhilarating sports car that embodies the essence of British luxury and performance. Renowned for its striking design, thrilling performance, and bespoke craftsmanship, the Vantage represents the epitome of automotive refinement, catering to enthusiasts seeking a driving experience like no other.\r\n\r\nFrom its sculpted body lines and aggressive stance to its iconic grille and signature LED headlights, the Aston Martin Vantage commands attention with its bold and unmistakable presence on the road. With its aerodynamic profile, muscular proportions, and distinctive styling cues, the Vantage exudes an aura of power, sophistication, and exclusivity that sets it apart from the competition.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'ll discover a meticulously crafted interior that blends exquisite materials, artisanal craftsmanship, and cutting-edge technology to create a luxurious and immersive driving environment. Premium leather upholstery, hand-stitched accents, and carbon fiber trim create a sense of opulence and refinement, while state-of-the-art infotainment systems, customizable driving modes, and advanced driver-assistance features ensure that every journey is both exhilarating and effortless.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s on the road where the Aston Martin Vantage truly comes to life. Powered by a potent twin-turbocharged V8 engine, the Vantage delivers blistering acceleration, razor-sharp handling, and a spine-tingling exhaust note that ignites the senses and leaves a lasting impression. Whether tearing up the track or cruising down the highway, the Vantage offers dynamic driving dynamics and precise performance that\'s guaranteed to thrill even the most discerning driving enthusiasts.\r\n\r\nIn addition to its exhilarating performance, the Aston Martin Vantage is also equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features and driver-assistive technologies to help keep you safe on every journey. From adaptive cruise control to lane-keeping assist, the Vantage provides peace of mind by actively helping to prevent accidents and protect occupants in the event of a collision.\r\n\r\nIn conclusion, the Aston Martin Vantage is more than just a car – it\'s a symbol of luxury, performance, and craftsmanship. With its timeless design, thrilling performance, and unparalleled refinement, the Vantage offers a driving experience that\'s as exhilarating as it is unforgettable. So why settle for anything less? Experience the Aston Martin Vantage and discover the true meaning of automotive excellence.',	'2024-08-07 07:04:00',	'images/Aston-Martin-Vantage(1).jpg'),
(12357,	19,	6,	'Chevrolet Camaro SS/ZL1:',	'Introducing the Chevrolet Camaro SS/ZL1, the pinnacle of American muscle car performance and exhilaration. Renowned for its breathtaking power, track-ready capabilities, and iconic design, the Camaro SS/ZL1 represents the epitome of automotive performance, catering to enthusiasts seeking an adrenaline-fueled driving experience like no other.\r\n\r\nFrom its aggressive stance and muscular proportions to its aerodynamic body lines and distinctive styling cues, the Chevrolet Camaro SS/ZL1 makes a bold statement with its commanding presence on the road. With its sculpted hood, wide grille, and aggressive front fascia, the Camaro SS/ZL1 exudes an aura of power, performance, and confidence that commands attention wherever it goes.\r\n\r\nStep inside, and you\'ll find a driver-focused cockpit that combines race-inspired design with cutting-edge technology and comfort features. Premium materials, ergonomic controls, and intuitive technology interfaces create a dynamic and immersive driving environment that puts you in complete control, while supportive seating, advanced connectivity options, and customizable driving modes ensure that every journey is both exhilarating and comfortable.\r\n\r\nBut it\'s on the road where the Chevrolet Camaro SS/ZL1 truly shines. Powered by a high-performance V8 engine, the Camaro SS/ZL1 delivers breathtaking acceleration, razor-sharp handling, and a thunderous exhaust note that ignites the senses and leaves a lasting impression. Whether tearing up the track or cruising down the highway, the Camaro SS/ZL1 offers blistering performance, precise handling, and unmatched thrills that push the boundaries of what\'s possible on four wheels.\r\n\r\nIn addition to its track-ready performance, the Chevrolet Camaro SS/ZL1 is also equipped with a range of advanced performance technologies and driver-assistive features to help you maximize your driving experience while staying safe on the road. From magnetic ride control to performance traction management, the Camaro SS/ZL1 provides the ultimate combination of performance and peace of mind for drivers who demand the very best.',	'2025-01-01 05:09:00',	'images/2024-chevrolet-camaro-ss-collectors-edition-1-647e1933c6c20.jpg');

